rows.label: qst620201_msg0001
rows.name: Just look at that, would yeh?

rows.label: qst620201_msg0002
rows.name:
This field were growin' mountains of
produce, but now it's picked clean as
t' Praetor's hanky.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0003
rows.name:
If the harvest is over, that's hardly...
Oh. That's not it, is it?

rows.label: qst620201_msg0004
rows.name: No, t'isn't.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0005
rows.name:
It's daylight robbery, it is. Some villain
came in't night and robbed me veg. Not
me neighbor's, mind... Just mine.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0006
rows.name:
A theft this bare-faced cannot
be forgiven!

rows.label: qst620201_msg0007
rows.name:
This man has been breaking his back
here all day, rain or shine! How dare
someone steal the fruit of his sweat?!

rows.label: qst620201_msg0008
rows.name:
Steady on, lad. You make it sound right
unappetizing when you put it like that...
...And I don't work all that 'ard either...

rows.label: qst620201_msg0009
rows.name:
'Tis of no import. A theft is a theft.
The act of a villainous man.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0010
rows.name: Why do you assume it's a man...?

rows.label: qst620201_msg0011
rows.name:
Man, Tirkin, or monster, the point
still stands.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0012
rows.name:
Whoever the transgressor, their
punishment shall be sure and swift...

rows.label: qst620201_msg0013
rows.name: Vasara!

rows.label: qst620201_msg0014
rows.name:
It's no use. That guy doesn't listen to
a word anyone says...

rows.label: qst620201_msg0015
rows.name:
Me, on the other hand? I'll go house to
house, door to door until I've heard
EVERYONE'S story!

rows.label: qst620201_msg0016
rows.name: Maybe there'll be a witness...

rows.label: qst620201_msg0017
rows.name:
Or maybe I'll find the perp and my
righteousness'll move them to confess
their crime and beg forgiveness!

rows.label: qst620201_msg0018
rows.name: So... Off I go!

rows.label: qst620201_msg0019
rows.name: ...How exasperating.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0020
rows.name:
Those two are like water and oil...
But at least they're both on the
right side of justice.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0021
rows.name:
I think I'll stand guard here at the field.
The thief may yet come back to steal
what produce remains...

rows.label: qst620201_msg0022
rows.name:
What do you think?
Does that sound like a plan?

rows.label: qst620201_msg0023
rows.name:
I thank you. Leave this job to me, then,
and I promise you I won't let you down.

rows.label: qst620201_msg0024
rows.name:
...And the rest of yeh'll go look for
the vegetable thief? Is that right?

rows.label: qst620201_msg0025
rows.name:
Thanks for that.
Good fortune to yeh.
